OL,5,FRunning one marathon is enough of a
OL,6,Fchallenge but for one runner it is far
OL,7,Ffrom his first.
OL,9,FWhen he crosses the finish line of the
OL,10,Fon Sunday, Gary Howells, 43, will have
OL,11,Fcompleted his 105th race.
OL,13,FHe will be completing the gruelling
OL,14,Fdistance to raise money for Welsh
OL,15,Fcharity Tenovus after losing a friend
OL,16,Fand fellow athlete from his home town
OL,17,Fto the disease last year.
