OL,5,FGary will not be competing alone,
OL,6,Fthough, with a dozen others from the
OL,7,Frunning group he set up joining him to
OL,8,Ffundraise for the same cause.
OL,10,FThe 43-year-old initially got into
OL,11,Frunning in 2012 after leaving the as
OL,12,Fhe settled back into civilian life,
OL,13,Fbecoming an electrical engineer
OL,14,Fworking on wind turbines.
