OL,5,FIt was six years later, running the
OL,6,Finfamous Marathon De Sables - an
OL,7,Fexhausting seven marathons in six days
OL,8,Facross the Sahara Desert - that Gary
OL,9,Fhad a "light bulb" moment, deciding to
OL,10,Fset up the Peak Performance Wales
OL,11,Frunning club and make the sport his
OL,12,Ffull-time job.
OL,14,FGary explained: "It was a light bulb
OL,15,Fmoment out there, and I just wanted to
OL,16,Fturn my ability to run marathons into
OL,17,Fa career.
