OL,5,FThe club is not just a job for Gary
OL,6,Fthough. He said: "Running gives me
OL,7,Flife challenges, it gives me goals, it
OL,8,Fkeeps me fit, and it keeps me mentally
OL,9,Fstimulated.
OL,11,F"It's given me a job, obviously, but
OL,12,Fit's also given me a running family."
OL,14,FTalking about the satisfaction he
OL,15,Ftakes from his work, he said: "I love
OL,16,Fthe satisfaction of seeing these guys,
OL,17,Fsome of whom are 60 years of age,
OL,18,Frunning with me.
