OL,5,F"It's part of what they pay me for and
OL,6,Fwhy they turn up every week. It's an
OL,7,Fexperience we'll be talking about for
OL,8,Fyears to come."
OL,10,FThe group decided to raise money for
OL,11,FTenovus following the death of
OL,12,FLlanelli local and avid runner Wayne
OL,13,FEvans, who lost his life to pancreatic
OL,14,Fcancer last year.
OL,16,FGary said: "Two other people in the
OL,17,Fclub got skin cancer last year, so
OL,18,Frunning it for Tenovus Cancer Care
OL,19,Fmeans a lot. We've raised #25K so far,
OL,20,Fbut we are hoping for so much more on
OL,21,Fthe day."
