OL,5,FHe added that when the runners
OL,6,Finevitably hit 'the wall' that comes
OL,7,Fwith running such a long way, Wayne
OL,8,Fwill be their inspiration to keep
OL,9,Fgoing.
OL,11,F"We are ready to go and when it gets
OL,12,Ftough at the end, we'll be thinking of
OL,13,FWayne and what he went through for 12
OL,14,Fmonths with his chemo and treatment,"
OL,15,FGary explained.
OL,17,FHe added: "We'll have 6 miles to go,
OL,18,Fand he'll be our inspiration. His
OL,19,Fmemory will pull us along. It's going
OL,20,Fto be magical."
