OL,5,FThe former military man said the group
OL,6,Fis "bouncing" ahead of the race on
OL,7,FSunday, with everyone "feeling fit and
OL,8,Fhealthy."
OL,10,FThe London Marathon will not be the
OL,11,Flast challenge Gary sets himself, with
OL,12,Fhis sights firmly fixed on even
OL,13,Ftougher races in the future.
OL,15,FHe said: "I want to run marathons in
OL,16,FKenya, Ethiopia and America, not just
OL,17,FBoston and Chicago and New York.
